                            <comment id="14199628" author="jimjh" created="Thu, 6 Nov 2014 02:08:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Reproduced with `spark-1.1.0-bin-hadoop2.4` on EMR.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14203631" author="jimjh" created="Sat, 8 Nov 2014 22:03:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Line 223 in &lt;tt&gt;org/apache/spark/deploy/yarn/ClientBase.java&lt;/tt&gt; seems like a good spot.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;    def prepareLocalResources(...) = {&lt;br/&gt;
        val cachedSecondaryJarLinks = ListBuffer.empty[String]&lt;br/&gt;
        ...&lt;br/&gt;
    }&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The datanucleus jars that need to be added are: datanucleus-api-jdo-3.2.1.jar, datanucleus-core-3.2.2.jar, datanucleus-rdbms-3.2.1.jar&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14209429" author="apachespark" created="Thu, 13 Nov 2014 07:28:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;User &apos;jimjh&apos; has created a pull request for this issue:&lt;br/&gt;
